{"tid":1357211,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"＜新轉機＞發大警黑單嘢推到成立獨立調查委員會","createTime":"2019-07-23T16:23:37.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-24T07:24:27.000Z","uid":59563,"like":37,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"ed4b5c7b4160cc8a37f0f75eed69e750a91ec1ca","tid":1357211,"uid":59563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T16:23:37.000Z","msg":"我知元朗單嘢花生指數係高，但我哋唔可以再愈行愈偏。民鬥民只會搞到自己內傷<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n最佳嘅做法係無論做乜嘢運動都好，都要連返上5大訴求度<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n2個月嚟搞咗咁多次遊行，唯獨係呢次出動哂咁多司局人員出嚟交代!除咗中聯辦仲有就係ー<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">警黑合作</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n大家心知肚明，condom 仔同牛屎佬夾好哂，雖然話吹雞條妖罪大惡極姐，但警黑合作咁好好嘅題材我哋唔可以放過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n今次唔同以前，打9義士佢可以一昧死撐話係執法，佢執法上有冇不當呢下好灰色，佢死口唔認我哋要入佢比較難<br />\n<br />\n但係!!!!!! <br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: maroon;\"><strong>元朗單嘢警察公然放棄執法，令社會陷入保安真空嘅狀態!!!!!完全失去作為執法者保護市民嘅作用!!!!!</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n拎住呢一個point 打，點都易入過係義士個邊出發<br />\n<br />\n政治遊戲好現實，就位就入，唔好捨易取難<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n外務文宣可以搞恐怖襲擊，內務就搞警隊集體失職(可以再吹大啲"},{"pid":"a63528e24f1f70422badfd1e41141a79b932e45f","tid":1357211,"uid":190716,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T16:27:02.000Z","msg":"啱，呢個係好機會<br />\n而且今日香港總商會都支持成立獨立調查委員會<br />\n有商界支持成事機會大好多"},{"pid":"d25fbf4779270b80341d4c1393f0696ce7cea8d9","tid":1357211,"uid":59563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a63528e24f1f70422badfd1e41141a79b932e45f","tid":1357211,"uid":190716,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T16:27:02.000Z","msg":"啱，呢個係好機會<br />\n而且今日香港總商會都支持成立獨立調查委員會<br />\n有商界支持成事機會大好多"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T16:32:56.000Z","msg":"成日講打民意戰<br />\n今次真係好機會<br />\n有咁慘講到咁慘，吹到好傍惶無助<br />\n對警隊冇哂信心，合理懷疑警黑合作<br />\n加上大西北一路以嚟都係牛屎佬大過警權<br />\n7成真3成吹，彈出又彈入<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"22ea70d488766ed126c9b9d110bd85e501da553e","tid":1357211,"uid":59563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T16:36:19.000Z","msg":"集思廣益諗諗佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n捉到鹿唔識脫角會後悔一世㗎<br />\n<br />\n何妖自有人收佢，我哋唔好浪費時間係呢個妖物身上啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0a1ca73ee6f407378ed34024918c6623cd5a67b0","tid":1357211,"uid":59563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T16:36:49.000Z","msg":"推一推"},{"pid":"c22a8d89c65c10bfaf0e3dce3e0018dc0c58b368","tid":1357211,"uid":165683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a63528e24f1f70422badfd1e41141a79b932e45f","tid":1357211,"uid":190716,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T16:27:02.000Z","msg":"啱，呢個係好機會<br />\n而且今日香港總商會都支持成立獨立調查委員會<br />\n有商界支持成事機會大好多"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T16:37:39.000Z","msg":"同意"},{"pid":"1eeec946704309a51f89b11b4a2f93dd5a0941b7","tid":1357211,"uid":165683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T16:38:16.000Z","msg":"逐個搞"},{"pid":"f9b7510cf35c54ede9b012a6a13d51bbc14d86f3","tid":1357211,"uid":285536,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ed4b5c7b4160cc8a37f0f75eed69e750a91ec1ca","tid":1357211,"